{"tid":1048653,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"個肚係唔係生蟲","createTime":"2019-03-05T20:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T09:15:25.000Z","uid":200527,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4f38e6e52e2a809a8876bec14962581d51283f1e","tid":1048653,"uid":200527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T20:24:54.000Z","msg":"最近幾日容易肚餓咗，個肚脹脹地<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間唔中肚痛下（大概一日兩三次度啦），<br />\n不過自己本身都係腸胃差嘅人所以冇咩點為意。<br />\n<br />\n好啦到今日下午兩點幾左右，係屋企廁所屙屎，<br />\n屙完之後好正常都會睇到自己舊屎啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知見到舊屎上面有d白色嘅物體，排列得好整齊，<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就喺度諗自己最近係唔係食咗粟米之類消化唔到嘅嘢啦&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n點知就喺呢刻，<br />\n我見到舊屎d白色嘢喺度郁&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為自己眼花，雖然嚇到企到好遠但仍然繼續觀察，<br />\n屌仲繼續郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係馬桶入面d水流動搞到舊屎鬱定真係d白色嘢郁啦下&hellip;<br />\n總之立即開咗少少廁所門，同男朋友求救叫佢喺廳拎紙巾俾我啦（要自己拎紙巾就要望多次舊屎，而當時已經就黎嘔）<br />\n<br />\n跟住夜晚食完嘢，翻屋企嘅時候順道買花塔糖黎食&hellip;<br />\n食完三粒宜家肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家覺得我等陣會見到d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1047e6596069ec901675f983e1127b70d1dd6d7c","tid":1048653,"uid":200527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T20:30:31.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee956ce2802a4334fff0a044a84c9bee58d2b1e","tid":1048653,"uid":232065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T20:38:29.000Z","msg":"唔係生蟲，絕症黎"},{"pid":"c7d96f9233b0e1250d94f9c0f73ea5b1e0fc9d61","tid":1048653,"uid":201943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T20:40:22.000Z","msg":"屎忽窿有冇好痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074f327a8f7ad90db70e14515a68864c31213ff6","tid":1048653