00Z","msg":"樓主今日痾多次睇睇有無多啲野出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c31455fdc13677940a83e9d4fb954e92c3d2e3","tid":1048653,"uid":129142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:24:20.000Z","msg":"隔住mon 都feel 到好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主真係辛苦哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名睇發展 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af67337c24500d015cc9571b8b03fa65adf752b","tid":1048653,"uid":223672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:29:33.000Z","msg":"要屙幾耐先屙得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2049c5d8eb38b8285239f5b18e0779864d5dd5fa","tid":1048653,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f38e6e52e2a809a8876bec14962581d51283f1e","tid":1048653,"uid":200527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T20:24:54.000Z","msg":"最近幾日容易肚餓咗，個肚脹脹地<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間唔中肚痛下（大概一日兩三次度啦），<br />\n不過自己本身都係腸胃差嘅人所以冇咩點為意。<br />\n<br />\n好啦到今日下午兩點幾左右，係屋企廁所屙屎，<br />\n屙完之後好正常都會睇到自己舊屎啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知見到舊屎上面有d白色嘅物體，排列得好整齊，<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就喺度諗自己最近係唔係食咗粟米之類消化唔到嘅嘢啦&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n點知就喺呢刻，<br />\n我見到舊屎d白色嘢喺度郁&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為自己眼花，雖然嚇到企到好遠但仍然繼續觀察，<br />\n屌仲繼續郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係馬桶入面d水流動搞到舊屎鬱定真係d白色嘢郁啦下&hellip;<br />\n總之立即開咗少少廁所門，同男朋友求救叫佢喺廳拎紙巾俾我啦（要自己拎紙巾就要望多次舊屎，而當時已經就黎嘔）<br />\n<br />\n跟住夜晚食完嘢，翻屋企嘅時候順道買花塔糖黎食&hellip;<br />\n食完三粒宜家肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家覺得我等陣會見到d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:33:42.000Z","msg":"影張相睇下"}]}